My husband I love this recipe. I've made it a few times now and it's our favourite mussel recipe. It's easy to make and mussels are always available and fairly inexpensive. I cook it exactly like the recipe. I find that the acidity of the wine and lemon do not bother me at all after the mussels and sauce are cooked. I love lemon. I agree with other reviewers and would not recommend using light coconut milk.

