Rating: 4
Terrific mussel dish - even my typically non-mussel eating wife gobbled these down. We substituted coconut cream for the milk and didn't have any shallots and the dish was still delicious. The mussels REALLY absorb the flavors - they end up sweet and spicy at the same time. Don't skimp on the curry - it's not overpowering. Will definitely make again.